    "bundle": "5MHGWTMQOPWFB3YYQNOIMGZIE5YZV33K",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "809001009",
    "title": "ちょっとだけお傍で",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "<chrname>との日々にもひと区切り\r\nついたある日のこと。",
            "enText": "One day, after a break in her life \nwith <chrname>, she found herself in \nthe company of a young man who had \nbeen working for a long time.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "pathId": -7561788533661220686,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "たづなさんに誘われ、レース場へと\r\n観戦にやって来たのだが――",
            "enText": "Tazuna invited me to the race \ntrack to watch the race.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "pathId": 6893198762233735231,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "あっ。トレーナーさーん！\r\nこっちです、こっち！",
            "enText": "Oh. Trainer! This way, this way!",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 60,
            "pathId": -3680533799386935846,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "まだ集合時間前なのに、お早いですね！",
            "enText": "You're early, even though it's \nnot yet time to meet!",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 56,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "たづなさんこそ",
                    "enText": "Thank you Tazuna!",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 146,
                    "pathId": 6032016562870196340
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 178,
                    "pathId": -5792338811397831025
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1292146832193936566,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "ふふふっ、それはもう！\r\n待ちきれなくって、つい。",
            "enText": "Mmmm, that's it! I just couldn't wait.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 29,
                    "pathId": -8986073605801770261
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": -6556911340765332269
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4060353963456114266,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "それでは――さっそく行きましょうか！",
            "enText": "So - let's get on with it!",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 56,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 39,
                    "pathId": -2402908750758361576
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 67,
                    "pathId": -3385468290817769088
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7848060709672603380,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "はぁっ、今日は一段と盛り上がりましたね！\r\nさすがＧⅠレースの開催日です……！",
            "enText": "Haha, it's been an even more exciting \nday! That's what you'd expect from \na day of G1 racing…!",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 70,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "会場の熱気がすごかったですね",
                    "enText": "The enthusiasm of the audience \nwas incredible!",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": -66989754848137091
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 113,
                    "pathId": -5150964692812571704
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3690169223669026325,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "ええ、ええ！\r\n応援の声で地面が揺れてしまうほどで！",
            "enText": "Yes, yes! The ground shook \nwith the cheering!",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 8573109113212791359
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": 5509259471070465707
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6909891660320397081,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "この興奮、この感動――\r\nやはり、レースはいいものですね！",
            "enText": "All this excitement, all this emotion \n- it's good to be racing!",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ですね！",
                    "enText": "Yes!",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 53,
                    "pathId": 1911530074062006045
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": 8143924756096741150
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2209525113501809673,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "……あの、トレーナーさん。",
            "enText": "… Um, trainer.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 53,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 43,
                    "pathId": -1419090367734948756
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 64,
                    "pathId": 241244061146539851
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8022329718374444429,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "今日はお付き合いいただき、\r\nありがとうございました。",
            "enText": "Thank you for being with us today.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 62,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 46,
                    "pathId": 574352024031280473
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 73,
                    "pathId": -8434889328615379746
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7263922212983480674,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "トレーナーさんにはどうしても、\r\n改めてお礼を申し上げたくって。",
            "enText": "I just wanted to say thank \nyou again to my trainer.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "お礼？",
                    "enText": "Thank you?",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": -5521324671775629821
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -6044690285930862250
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -776109842405212247,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "ええ。",
            "enText": "Yes.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 46,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 57,
                    "pathId": -5905979330873610382
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 57,
                    "pathId": -6782704193755807242
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5974412018773982547,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "この3年間、<chrname>さんと共に、\r\n様々なレースを駆け抜けられましたね。",
            "enText": "Over the past three years, you and <chrname> \nhave been through a lot of races.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": -2084825451926178061
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 3178031897670285535
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2441905082681290503,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "観ていました、全て。現地でも、テレビでも、\r\nあなた方の活躍に胸を躍らせていました。",
            "enText": "I watched it all. I was there, I was on TV, \nI was excited by what you were doing.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 4930463484842977362
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -6595713100966138702
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": 8756076537178598562
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5199415423426014907,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "本当に――夢のような、\r\n奇跡の瞬間をたくさん見せていただきました。",
            "enText": "We had many miraculous moments, \nlike a dream.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 49,
                    "pathId": -4903180018812980817
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 6376814636992640520
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3189678454029523159,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "ですから、改めて。\r\n……感動を、ありがとうございます！",
            "enText": "So, once again. Thank you \nfor the… inspiration!",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 51,
                    "pathId": -7052314732302408229
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": 4042840527654414389
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2791518628658914048,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "そして……これからもどうかケガ無く無事に、\r\n未来へ向かって、走り続けてくださいね！",
            "enText": "And… please continue to run safely, \ninjury free, into the future!",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "はい！！",
                    "enText": "Yes!",
                    "nextBlock": 19
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 3787956886679298027
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -5274158504028426079
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4972004401894152563,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "いいお返事です♪",
            "enText": "Good reply…",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 50,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 22,
                    "pathId": 6779834287168737000
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": -2604807633025347710
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8851792988127374193,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "これからの活躍も、\r\nしっかり見守らせていただきますね。",
            "enText": "We will be keeping a close eye \non your future activities.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 51,
                    "pathId": -380095771423818210
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": 2629906681934038827
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8613215560721123088,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "……以前よりも、ちょっとだけお傍で♪",
            "enText": "… by a little more than before…",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 56,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 67,
                    "pathId": 5985449238407542989
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 67,
                    "pathId": 2981623127815451139
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6799915149090616886,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "のちに合流した<chrname>も一緒に、\r\nたづなさんとの観戦を楽しんだ。",
            "enText": "<chrname>, who joined us later in the day, \nenjoyed watching the game with Tazuna.",
